<!-- ==========================================================

Description:
Edit Note page template.

This view allows users to:
- Modify an existing note.
- Persist changes.
- Delete the note if needed.

Server Variables:
- noteId → Injected dynamically to identify the note
  being edited. Stored in a hidden input field for
  client-side reference.

Responsibilities:
- Render edit form structure.
- Provide fields for title and content modification.
- Expose note ID for update/delete operations.
- Support internationalization via data-i18n attributes.

Structure:
- Includes global header and footer partials.
- Organized using BEM methodology.
- Divided into form inputs and action buttons section.

Client-Side Behavior:
- Form submission triggers update logic (handled in editar.js).
- Delete button triggers note removal process.
- Note data is loaded dynamically via JavaScript.
- Validation and persistence handled client-side
  through Firebase or backend integration.

Dependencies:
- editar.js
- authState.js (if edit access depends on authentication)
- i18n system
- Global bundle.min.js

Notes:
- This template does not directly perform data updates.
- All CRUD operations are managed via frontend modules.
- Hidden note ID ensures secure reference without
  exposing sensitive data in visible fields.
========================================================== -->

<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="editar">
    <h2 class="editar__titulo" data-i18n="edit_note"></h2>

    <form class="editar__form" id="edit-form">
        <input type="hidden" id="note-id" value="<%= noteId %>">

        <label class="editar__tituloForm" data-i18n="title"></label>
        <input id="edit-title" class="editar__input" type="text">

        <label class="editar__contenidoForm" data-i18n="content"></label>
        <textarea id="edit-content" class="editar__textarea"></textarea>

        <div class="editar__actions">
            <button type="submit" class="editar__save-btn" data-i18n="saveEdit"></button>
            <button type="button" id="delete-note" class="editar__delete-btn" data-i18n="deleteEdit"></button>
        </div>
    </form>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>